
Disk Manager
------------

Disk Manager is a Pardus GUI application used for managing automatic
mount operations for your disks. It provides an easy interface to
configure. You do configure how your disk partitions will be
initialized at system startup. Disks are integrated into systemâ€™s
file system with this configuration. So that you do not have to mount
your disks manually again and again. Disk Manager also allows you to
mount or unmount your disk partitions.
